description: Best practices for Astro projects, focusing on islands and content.
globs: **/*.astro, src/content/config.ts
---

# Astro Best Practices

## 1. Islands Architecture
- **Zero-JS by Default:** Write components as static Astro components first.
- **Client Directives:** Only use client directives (e.g., `client:load`, `client:idle`) when client-side interactivity is **required**.
- **Pass Props:** Pass data as props from your server-side Astro component to your client-side Svelte/React/etc. island. Avoid data fetching inside a client island.

## 2. Content Collections
- **Use Collections:** All Markdown/MDX content must live in `src/content/`.
- **Define Schemas:** All collections MUST have a strict schema defined in `src/content/config.ts` using Zod.
